Gradients
This WebPage has 562 Gradients which have been taken from these website Web Gradients & UI Gradients.

Press Next & Previous Buttons to Navigate.

You can enter a number in the Input Box which is beside the set Button to move in the List.

Copy Button will copy CSS corresponding to the Gradient to the clipboard.

The Colors of the Random Gradient Colors are not saved once refreshed they are gone. So Copy soon if you like one

At last there is a Download Button which downloads the Gradient on Screen in PNG format.
